HEADWORD: Un-Mosaic
<hw>Un`-Mo*sa"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not according to
Moses; unlike Moses or his works.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>By this reckoning <qex>Moses</qex> should be most <qex>un
Mosaic</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unmothered</ent>⟦br⟧
